Task:
Identify and state concisely:
1. The cycle at which the assertion fires (this is cycle 1).  Also
   note the first cycle in 0..1 where a signal first deviates from
   its expected value.  If the assertion is a liveness time-out, report 1.
2. The signal(s) directly responsible for the assertion failure (name them exactly
